{{Jainism}}
'''Amritchandra''' (f. 10th-century CE) was a [[Digambara]] [[Jain]] [[Acharya]] who wrote commentaries on [[Samayasāra]], [[Pravachanasara]] and [[Pancastikayasara]].{{sfn|Vijay K Jain|2012|p=xiv}} He also wrote independent books of [[Puruşārthasiddhyupāya]] and [[Tattvartha Sara]].{{sfn|Finegan|1952|p=205}} He wrote in [[Sanskrit]] language.

